---
title: Bell Pepper Jack O'lanterns with mummified potatoes
description: Scary peppers stuffed with spiced mince and topped with melted cheese make for the perfect jarring Jack O'lanterns this spooky season.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R22_W44_IE_IESB28030-6_Main_F1_high-977379d5.jpg
